## 🎬 Code patterns

### Appwrite query format (CRITICAL):
```js
await appwriteList(APPWRITE.videosCollection, [
  JSON.stringify({ method: 'orderDesc', attribute: '$createdAt' }),
  JSON.stringify({ method: 'limit', values: [50] })
]);
```

### Edge Function helper (in `js/supabase.js`):
```js
export async function callEdgeFunction(functionName, payload = {}) {
  const { data: { session } } = await supabase.auth.getSession();
  if (!session) throw new Error('Not logged in');
  const url = `${SUPABASE_URL}/functions/v1/${functionName}`;
  // ... fetch with Bearer token ...
}
```

### Imports in `js/app.js` line 1:
```js
import { supabase, REACTIONS, timeAgo, initials, appwriteList, appwriteGet, APPWRITE, callEdgeFunction, BUNNY } from './supabase.js';
```

